{"id":"SIPEIBOJUE5","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["<size=51>私の側にいてくれる人<\/size>",1.5],["<size=51>私とともに戦ってくれる人<\/size>",3],["<size=51>私の思いをわかってくれる人<\/size>",4.5],["<size=51>でも、あの人達を失ってしまえば<\/size> ",6],["<size=51>私は、「私」でいられるのでしょうか――<\/size>",8]]},{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["小さな出来事\n\n<size=45>五　孤独感<\/size>",1]]},{"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"say":"母港・寮舎","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"悪い夢を見た。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"目が覚めると、周りには誰もいない……","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","dir":1,"say":"んっ……もうこの時間なの…？","nameColor":"#a9f548","bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403050,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"たしかに非番の日のこの時間だと、寮には誰もいないね。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"……よし","actor":403050,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ベッドでゴロゴロしながら、最近使い方を覚えたスマートフォンを取り出す。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"これなら、側にいなくてもみんなの様子がわかるね。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"「今日もジャベリン、弁当作り頑張りまーす！」","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ジャベリンちゃん……なんか元気な人だよね。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_r